name: "MVC Portlet with DS and JSP"
description: |
  Demonstrates how to 
    - build a portlet with Liferay MVC framework
    - use DS (Declarative Services) framework to register it
    - use JSPs for the view
displayFiles:
  - name: Documentation 
    highlighting: markdown 
    path: README.md
  - name: Portlet class
    highlighting: java 
    path: src/main/java/com/liferay/blade/samples/portlet/jsp/JSPPortlet.java
  - name: JSP
    highlighting: jsp 
    path: src/main/resources/META-INF/resources/view.jsp
  - name: Bnd configuration
    highlighting: yaml 
    path: bnd.bnd
  - name: Maven POM
    highlighting: xml 
    path: pom.xml
  - name: Gradle build
    highlighting: groovy 
    path: build.gradle
